    "title": "2014 Political Ad by Bold agenda PAC",
    "subject": "Bold agenda PAC; none; PAC; AMERICA; REPUBLICAN; common; agenda",
    "description": "Think campaign season is just about fighting? Take another look. There's a bold, smart, republican agenda were common sense puts results over politics. Lets get America back on the job. Help companies that invest in workers with a tax cut only after they bring jobs back from overseas. End common core, have you seen how ridiculous the new math is? We don't need DC and big companies forcing the common core on our kids. Terrorists depend on us buying foreign oil, lets get them out of the energy business by producing it here. We know human traffickers, terrorists, drugs and disease can cross our border at any time. Secure it. Now. And we can all agree, over the counter birth control is the smart thing to do. See? That wasn't so hard. And we're just getting started. Bold agenda PAC is responsible for the content of this message.",
